      "value": "<p>&gt;@UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.theme-features.Item.lNkqx1Eb6zm7iPuN]{Bestial Lineage}</p>\n<p>Your instincts lead you to flank foes and bring them down for the kill. When you @UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.rules.JournalEntry.Kjba2E3Ad5oMJ7hV.JournalEntryPage.X0cZZItDqyTDLhz2]{flank} an opponent, you gain a +2 bonus to your attack roll to perform the @UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.rules.JournalEntry.U37n5tY5hn1ctzQL.JournalEntryPage.R33uiOMesYP0ISWl#trip]{trip} combat maneuver against that opponent, in addition to the benefits of flanking. This bonus does not stack with other effects that grant you a bonus to perform the trip combat maneuver.</p>"
